@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Pay Fine
skinparam style strictuml

/' TEXT DESCRIPTION (Steps)
1. Member opens fines list.
2. Member selects a fine to pay.
3. System displays amount and payment methods.
4. Member confirms payment.
5. System sends payment request to payment service.
6. If payment succeeds, system records payment and marks fine paid.
7. System shows receipt; otherwise shows failure message.
'/

start
:Open fines list;
:Select Fine to pay;
:Display amount and methods;
:Confirm payment;
:Send payment request to Payment Service;

if (Payment successful?) then (Yes)
  :Record Payment;
  :Mark Fine as Paid;
  :Show receipt;
else (No)
  :Show payment failed;
endif

stop
@enduml